{"tid":913222,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企wifi訊號差問題","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T10:09:18.000Z","uid":202804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6dc9f8598e9096e0545781292745f31238aca8","tid":913222,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"屋企本身用r7000 (用左3,4年)  個router放係廳<br />\n已經對住個走廊<br />\n但隔左2間房, 訊號開始弱, 通常得番2格, 但實質延遲係好勁<br />\n(中間有主力牆)<br />\n想阿爸阿媽係房用可以訊號強d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身屋企個上網主線係廳到出, 但有lan線入牆連番入房<br />\n依家想加多個router放係房到<br />\n想問下個新router set做一個新既wifi點可唔可行?<br />\n同埋有無router係無咩燈?, 因為放係放既話訓覺唔想有光閃下閃下"},{"pid":"acef7d6947a07c858196dd2d534e279136806339","tid":913222,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"你行 mesh最好<br />\n用lan線連接主副<br />\n<br />\n可以同一個ssid行匀全屋"},{"pid":"0545639fa985277b22f0823da6610dad812aaca3","tid":913222,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acef7d6947a07c858196dd2d534e279136806339","tid":913222,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"你行 mesh最好<br />\n用lan線連接主副<br />\n<br />\n可以同一個ssid行匀全屋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"如果用mesh係咪最好用同型號既router?"},{"pid":"9a37bbeb6af3286d4737baf8225eb26041d63dcf","tid":913222,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0545639fa985277b22f0823da6610dad812aaca3","tid":913222,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acef7d6947a07c858196dd2d534e279136806339","tid":913222,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"你行 mesh最好<br />\n用lan線連接主副<br />\n<br />\n可以同一個ssid行匀全屋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"如果用mesh係咪最好用同型號既router?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"趁感恩節買隻 netgear ex3700"},{"pid":"5fdf5b8b0170c94d39ece9608e08434