like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ef3d2ef4007c4cff6c3be5fd0c4f07a25e11d99","tid":913222,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">1. 本身屋企個上網主線係廳到出\n2. 但有lan線入牆連番入房\n3. 依家想加多個router放係房到\n4. 想問下個新router set做一個新既wifi點</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n我同你差唔多 (1), (2).<br />\n<br />\n我試過 (3), (4)， 結果係 速度慢成六七倍 可能係router 過 router 慢咗啦 中間用 lan 線 都係慢超多 <br />\n<br />\n現在解決方法係將router放咗喺a位置，仲要係櫃頂最高。咁樣射過走廊入房，訊號幾好。不過更好係放喺b位/c位走廊頭。睇下你邊個位方便啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxFSCWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxFSCWe.png&h=9b6d1247&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dc12fcff5c51d506486c3d327e42a83ebd9d572","tid":913222,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"我就買左個homeplug"}]}